   - fatigue      → iron (oxygen transport), magnesium (mitochondria), vitaminD, b6
   - cramps       → magnesium (muscle relax), omega3 (anti-prostaglandin), calcium
   - pms          → magnesium, b6 (serotonin synthesis), calcium, omega3
   - bloating     → fiber (gut motility), calcium (gut contraction)
   - mood         → b6 (serotonin), omega3 (brain DHA), magnesium (GABA)
   - acne         → omega3 (anti-sebum inflam.), zinc (mapped via iron tag), fiber (estrogen clearance)
   - sleep        → magnesium (GABA activation), b6 (melatonin), calcium
   - lowenergy    → iron, vitaminD, b6, fiber (blood sugar)
*/
